PN,43801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FThe three members of the Royal Navy
OL,7,Fwho were killed when a their
OL,8,Fhelicopter crashed into a Devon field
OL,9,Fhave been named.
OL,11,FBritain's only female Royal Navy
OL,12,Fcommando was one of the three victims
OL,13,Fof the Devon helicopter crash.
OL,15,FLt Lily-Mae Fisher, 31, who was based
OL,16,Fin Yeovil, Somerset, was a member of
OL,17,Fthe Royal Navy from May 2019 before
OL,18,Fher death in the incident.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FThe crash took place during her final
OL,7,Fassessment of flying training and she
OL,8,Fwas due to be awarded her Pilot's
OL,9,Fwings in June 2026.
OL,11,FShe described it as a "massive
OL,12,Fprivilege and a huge honour to serve
OL,13,Fmy country" ` with her achievement as
OL,14,Fthe only British female Royal Navy
OL,15,Fcommando being praised by Nato.
OL,17,F31-year-old Lily-Mae shared her
OL,18,Fexperience in the Royal Navy and
OL,19,Fadvice for those wanting to follow in
OL,20,Fher footsteps on social media.
OL,26,@sD@WOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FIn June 2022, she became the first
OL,7,Fserving female Royal Navy Commando.
OL,9,FShe shared photos and videos of
OL,10,Fherself online, proudly wearing her
OL,11,Fgreen beret, which is worn exclusively
OL,12,Fby those who pass the commando course.
OL,14,FAt the time, she shared a photograph
OL,15,Fof herself on her social media saying:
OL,17,F"In this photo I was so broken, 16
OL,18,Fweeks of relentless physical and
OL,19,Fmental challenges. Just being thankful
OL,20,Feach evening I was still there,
OL,21,Funinjured, and passing.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,F"There were so many times I thought,
OL,7,F'I don't know if I can pass' or 'this
OL,8,Fis the hardest thing I have ever
OL,9,Fdone'. But mental resilience, the
OL,10,Fstubbornness, the drive, to achieve
OL,11,Fwhat I set out to do was stronger than
OL,12,Fany of those doubts.
OL,14,F"Knowing that earning the Green Beret
OL,15,Fwill open doors into more advanced
OL,16,Fcourses, more opportunities, and also
OL,17,Fto overcome the fear of failure, the
OL,18,Ffirst time truly in my life where I
OL,19,Fwas terrified of failing, everyday."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FThe trainee royal navy pilot had a
OL,7,Flarge following online where she
OL,8,Fregularly shared her pride at
OL,9,Fsucceeding in a stereotypically male
OL,10,Fworld.
OL,12,FLast year, she shared a post, writing:
OL,13,F"After 5 years of struggles with
OL,14,Fapplying to the military, plus another
OL,15,F6.5 years of flying, holdovers, tough
OL,16,Fcourses, amazing opportunities,
OL,17,Fsporting achievements, and incredible
OL,18,Fpeople by my side... I finally stepped
OL,19,Finto the cockpit of a Merlin 
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,F"It's been a long road, but I'm so
OL,7,Fproud and happy to be here!"
OL,9,FPaying tribute to her, her family
OL,10,Fsaid: "Lily-Mae was an extraordinary
OL,11,Fwoman, daughter, sister, and partner.
OL,12,FTo say she was full of life is an
OL,13,Funderstatement: she took every
OL,14,Fopportunity to push her limits,
OL,15,Fachieve more, and bring out the best
OL,16,Fin those around her.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@\O]rD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,F"We are so proud of everything she
OL,7,Faccomplished. She has left an
OL,8,Fimmeasurable hole in our lives, and in
OL,9,Fall the lives she has touched and
OL,10,Finspired. The family kindly ask for
OL,11,Ftime and space at this difficult time."
OL,13,FLiutenant Commander Chris Gayson also
OL,14,Flost his life in the crash.
OL,16,FThe 42-year-old had studied for a
OL,17,FMasters in Aerospace Engineering at
OL,18,Fthe University of Bath before gaining
OL,19,Fhis Pilot Wings in October 2012.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@gO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FHe had a varied career with the Royal
OL,7,FNavy, including serving with the 845
OL,8,FNAS, taking on the role of Air Safety
OL,9,FOfficer before becoming Lieutenant
OL,10,FCommander in 2020 when he assumed the
OL,11,Frole of Senior Pilot of the Sixty Sqn.
OL,13,FHis family paid tribute to him saying:
OL,14,F"Chris was an extremely kind and
OL,15,Fgentle family man who loved his entire
OL,16,Ffamily dearly.
OL,18,F"He was also passionate about and
OL,19,Fdedicated to his job in the Royal
OL,20,FNavy."
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Royal Navy said:
OL,7,F"An utmost professional, his
OL,8,Fleadership of the Operational
OL,9,FConversion Flight was exemplary, and
OL,10,Fhis loss is a huge blow to the Royal
OL,11,FNavy, Force, and Squadron."
OL,13,FAlso killed in the crash was Petty
OL,14,FOfficer Owen Green.
OL,16,FThe 24-year-old joined the Royal Navy
OL,17,Fin January of 2022 and rapidly
OL,18,Fprogressed through the ranks.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FHe played a key role in major
OL,7,Fexercises, including in demanding
OL,8,Farctic conditions where he accumulate
OL,9,Fthe highest-flying hours among his
OL,10,Fpeers.
OL,12,FHis family said: "Losing Owen has left
OL,13,Fus all devastated. His life was far
OL,14,Ftoo short, and our hearts will forever
OL,15,Fbe broken.
OL,17,F"He was a caring and devoted son,
OL,18,Fbrother, grandson, and partner to
OL,19,FIona, whom he loved and cherished.
OL,26,@tD@ROUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,F"His kindness, warmth, and character
OL,7,Ftouched everyone who knew him. We are
OL,8,Fso proud of him achieving his life's
OL,9,Fgoal to serve in the Royal Navy as a
OL,10,FJunglie Aircrewman and are grateful
OL,11,Ffor the joy he brought into ours and
OL,12,FIona's lives.
OL,14,F"He is so loved and will remain in our
OL,15,Fhearts forever.
OL,17,FDefence Secretary John Healey
OL,18,Fdescribed all three as "dedicated and
OL,19,Fhighly valued members of their
OL,20,Fsquadrons who embodied the best of our
OL,21,FArmed Forces".
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@XOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FThe Merlin Mk4 helicopter crashed into
OL,7,Fa field during a training exercise
OL,8,Fover Dartmoor, leaving the aircraft
OL,9,Fcompletely destroyed.
OL,11,FMembers of the UK armed forces have
OL,12,Fstarted paying tribute to the three
OL,13,Fkilled in the crash.
OL,15,FCommanding Officer of Commando
OL,16,FHelicopter Force, Colonel Will
OL,17,FPenkman, said: "It is a tragedy that
OL,18,Fwe lost three members of the CHF
OL,19,Ffamily yesterday.
OL,26,@yD@POU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,F"Cherished members of the force with
OL,7,Fbright futures ahead of them, they
OL,8,Fwere all highly committed
OL,9,Fprofessionals infused with the Junglie
OL,10,Fspirit of the force.
OL,12,F"Their loss leaves a terrible gap in
OL,13,Four hearts and my thoughts go out to
OL,14,Ftheir family and friends who dearly
OL,15,Floved them."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Ministry of
OL,7,FDefence said: "It is with great
OL,8,Fsadness that we can confirm the deaths
OL,9,Fof Lieutenant Commander Chris Gayson
OL,10,Fand Lieutenant Lily-Mae Fisher of 846
OL,11,FNavy Air Squadron, and Petty Officer
OL,12,FOwen Green of 845 Navy Air Squadron,
OL,13,Fwho died in Devon during routine
OL,14,Ftraining activity on 3 June."
OL,16,FThe Ministry of Defence (MoD) said Lt
OL,17,FFisher, Lt Cdr Gayson and Petty
OL,18,FOfficer Green were based in Yeovil,
OL,19,FSomerset ` with the first two serving
OL,20,Fwith 846 Naval Air Squadron and the
OL,21,Flatter with 845 Naval Air Squadron.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FAlso paying tribute to the trio,
OL,7,FCommander of Joint Aviation Command,
OL,8,FAir Vice-Marshal Lee Turner, said:
OL,9,F"The loss of three deeply capable and
OL,10,Fprofessional aviators during the
OL,11,Ftragic incident yesterday is the cause
OL,12,Fof profound sadness across the Joint
OL,13,FAviation Command and the Commando
OL,14,FHelicopter Force in particular.
OL,16,F"They will be greatly missed, and our
OL,17,Fthoughts are with the families and all
OL,18,Fthose affected."
OL,26,@qD@AOUxD@AOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FThe aircraft crashed into a field just
OL,7,Fbefore 4am on Wednesday 3 June at
OL,8,FSourton Down, near Okehampton.
OL,10,FThe scene of the crash is close to
OL,11,FOkehampton battle camp, a military
OL,12,Ffacility on the edge of Dartmoor which
OL,13,Fhas been used for training Merlin
OL,14,Fhelicopter crews from the Commando
OL,15,FHelicopter Force.
OL,17,FIt lies between the Royal Navy's air
OL,18,Fbases at RNAS Yeovilton in Somerset
OL,19,Fand RNAS Culdrose in Cornwall.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,FIn a statement, the head of the Navy,
OL,7,FGeneral Sir Gwyn Jenkins said: "I am
OL,8,Fdeeply saddened to share the news that
OL,9,Fthree crew members onboard a Royal
OL,10,FNavy Merlin Mk4 helicopter have died
OL,11,Fafter it crashed in the early hours of
OL,12,Fthis morning near Sourton, Devon.
OL,14,F"I know this will come as a huge shock
OL,15,Fto all in our Naval community, and my
OL,16,Fdeepest condolences go out to the
OL,17,Ffamilies, friends and loved ones
OL,18,Fimpacted by this tragedy.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780924279
OL,3,CThree Royal Navy helicopter crash
OL,4,Cvictims named
OL,6,F"I would like to thank Devon and
OL,7,FCornwall Police and the search and
OL,8,Frescue teams who responded to the
OL,9,Fincident this morning.
OL,11,F"An investigation is under way and
OL,12,Ffurther updates will be provided in
OL,13,Fdue course."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/18
